nenjinile is a 1999 tamil action thriller film directed and co-written by s. a. chandrasekhar . the film features vijay and isha koppikar in the lead roles , while sonu sood , sriman and manivannan play supporting roles . the film 's music is composed by deva , and the film opened in june 1999 to a mixed response at box office . this movie was dubbed in hindi as dilwala baazigar and in telugu as sarathi .